'''Nasib Farah''' (yavutse 1981), ni  umunyasomaliya-[[Danimarike|Danish]] .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyaneMy COUSIN  PIRATE ,''Warrior from the North'' and ''Lost warrior'' .  Usibye gukora amafilime, ni umunyamakuru, umusemuzi, umuyobozi ushinzwe umusaruro, umufasha wigisha akaba n'umugiraneza.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye muri [[Somaliya]] mu 1981. Mu 1990 yahunze [[Mogadishu]] n'umuryango we nyuma y'intambara yo muri [[Somaliya]]. Icyakora, yabuze umuryango we igihe yarokoka hanyuma ahungira ku mupaka yerekeza muri [[Etiyopiya]], mbere yo guhaguruka mu [[Budage]] arangije atura muri [[Danimarike]].  Ku ikubitiro yari impunzi itaraherekejwe nyuma akurira mu kigo cya Croix Rouge cyo muri [[Danemarike]] Avnstrup hafi ya Lejre. 

Yashakanye n’umugore wo muri [[Danemarke]], babyarana abana. 

== Umwuga ==
Yatoje nk'umucuruzi kandi akora nk'umunyamakuru wigenga imyaka mike. Nyuma yaje gushinga umuryango udaharanira inyungu wibanda ku gufasha abandi basore bo muri [[Somaliya]] binyuze mu kwigisha no nyuma y’ishuri. Yifashishije iryo shyirahamwe kugira ngo agaragaze ibyamubayeho, Farah yatangije gahunda ya tereviziyo y'abaturage yitwa 'Qaran TV' ku baturage ba [[Somaliya]] muri [[Danimarike]]. 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, Farah yagize uruhare runini muri filime My COUSIN  PIRATE, iyobowe na Christian Sønderby Jepsen. Icyakora buri gihe yakeneraga gukora nk'umuyobozi aho kuba umukinnyi. 

Muri 2015, yakoze ''filime yambere ya Warriors kuva mumajyaruguru'' . Yamamaye cyane kandi yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Muri 2018, yayoboye documentaire ya kabiri ''Lost Warrior ari'' kumwe n'umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Danemarike]] Søren Steen Jespersen

